{"tid":444184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】車cam影低愛驅遭刮花一刻 車主冀目擊者助緝兇","createTime":"2017-10-22T09:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T09:31:10.000Z","uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"adff29ebd389782dd4162b199eec90213a3001fa","tid":444184,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nqCnIKcH4MA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnqCnIKcH4MA&d=QyXU194jRvXZQ7BW7U48ZwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4d9a5a59\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nqCnIKcH4MA</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/174531_2adf4297739c341218dabf26994213d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F174531_2adf4297739c341218dabf26994213d9.jpg&h=b515cbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/174531_79687aacc39b9ae3452c37f01f82055a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F174531_79687aacc39b9ae3452c37f01f82055a.jpg&h=8c2e3fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n        屯門有車主愛驅遭人蓄意刮花！有網民在facebook上載相片及片段，可見一名男子途經其私家車車頭時，用物件在車頭蓋刮了一道長長刮痕，該網民已報警，並表示希望附近的商舖及事發時在附近的車主可協助緝兇。<br />\n<br />\n　　該網民昨在facebook貼文稱，事發在昨晚10時23分，屯門虹橋青翠徑發生。車cam影片所見，一名體型略胖，事發時身穿黑色Polo恤的男子行近事主車頭時，右手疑拿著物件，並放在車頭蓋上，劃出一道刮痕後離開，期間曾回頭一看。貼文者亦上載一張照片，顯示車頭蓋上有明顯的白色長刮痕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 𠝹一𠝹就搞到車主無左幾皮野"},{"pid":"2f255a6a0e5012ea529940bf575e2b6e41206d3d","tid":444184,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"違例泊車？"},{"pid":"0def01afc4f74d877d105587e7b99d904357975f","tid":444184,"uid":17103,"like":0,"di